graph TB
    subgraph Phase1 [1-init.ps1]
        A1[Create folder structure]
        A2[Create symlink bindings]
        A3[Write config files]
        A1 --> A2 --> A3
    end

    subgraph Phase2 [2-deps.ps1]
        B1[Install system dependencies<br>Git, Python, Ollama, FFmpeg]
        B2[Set environment variables]
        B1 --> B2
    end

    subgraph Phase3 [3-apps.ps1]
        C1[Install ComfyUI + Open Web UI]
        C2[Auto-detect GPU<br>→ select backend]
        C3a[CUDA backend<br>NVIDIA]
        C3b[ROCm backend<br>AMD RDNA2-4<br>Python 3.12]
        C3c[DirectML backend<br>AMD RDNA1<br>Python 3.11]
        C3d[CPU fallback<br>Intel / no GPU]
        C4[Create venvs<br>Install Python packages]
        C5[Write model paths + launchers]
        
        C1 --> C2
        C2 --> C3a
        C2 --> C3b
        C2 --> C3c
        C2 --> C3d
        C3a --> C4
        C3b --> C4
        C3c --> C4
        C3d --> C4
        C4 --> C5
    end

    subgraph Phase4 [ai.ps1 - Daily Driver CLI]
        D1[ai start/stop/restart all]
        D2[ai status dashboard]
        D3[ai doctor diagnostics]
        D4[ai watch &lt;service&gt; logs]
        D5[ai install updates]
        D6[ai clean cache]
        D7[ai setup ports / env]
    end

    Phase1 --> Phase2
    Phase2 --> Phase3
    Phase3 --> Phase4

    style Phase1 fill:transparent,stroke:#4a9eff,stroke-width:2px,color:#333
